OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally sunny and warm or
OL,6,Fvery warm inland, but breezier than
OL,7,Frecently, especially along the coast
OL,8,Fwhere low cloud may develop at times.
OL,9,FTemperatures will be slightly cooler
OL,10,Fthan in recent days, especially along
OL,11,Fcoastal areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAnother warm night,
OL,14,Fespecially in large towns and cities,
OL,15,Fwith humid conditions persisting. Some
OL,16,Flargely clear skies but a chance of
OL,17,Fshowers or thundery outbreaks around
OL,18,Fdawn on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
