OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain soon
OL,6,Fclearing into the North Sea leading to
OL,7,Fanother very warm or hot day. Sunny
OL,8,Fspells and showers otherwise, heavy
OL,9,Fand potentially thundery in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStill
OL,13,Fvery warm on Saturday, with a chance
OL,14,Fof showers or thunderstorms. Breezy
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of rain pushing east on
OL,16,FSunday, cooler. Sunny spells and
OL,17,Fisolated showers on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
